Fun related trick:<p><pre><code>    $ cat test.c
    int compiler_supports_single_line_comments = 1 //*
    //*/ 2
    ;

    int main(void)
    {
        return compiler_supports_single_line_comments;
    }

    $ gcc test.c -o test && ./test ; echo $?
    1
    $ gcc -std=c89 test.c -o test && ./test ; echo $?
    0</code></pre>
